Subject: Re: [VB] Please help me with my 1500 .... -OR- .... 1600 DP

the motor should just bolt right into the bus. but you
will need to change some of the engine tin. just swap
out all the tin from the 1500 to the 1600 minus the
cylinder tins. and if any of the motors had dog house
style shroud, use it. hope this helps.

